{
  "stem": "888.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then there was these fellas from-- I think they came from [NON-ENGLISH] or somewhere, from their language.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were [NON-ENGLISH], you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were, you know-- what do you call them?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Tanners, who tanned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they, for some reason-- so he says to me, he says, why don't I give you a couple of candies?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, try to sell it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You sell it for so many zlotys, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So until there was-- so I used to sell it and make a few zlotys, you know, 10, 12 zlotys, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I couldn't-- we couldn't go there all the time, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But when I saw him, I knew where he was in camp to give him the money.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But then later on, you know, there was, from our hometown, you know, somebody, an overseer, who made him overseer.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He realized, you know, that I have candy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He says, give me a candy, give me a candy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So and of course, I was very honest, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I says to him, I says, I don't want any more candy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because he eats my candy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I won't be able to pay you back any money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I stopped that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then of course, then later on, we were working in different details, you know, like--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Plaszow, the Germans were-- first, they took us to details, you know, where we used to clean or dig, dig, you know, like ditches, and carry stones in these little carts, you know, on, on--",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, there was some wheelbarrow work, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But mainly they had, like, those lorries, you know, which you-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On tracks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
